<p>Tyler Hall, <a href="https://tyler.io/2025/11/alan/">annnouncing his new free Mac utility</a>:</p>
<blockquote><p>
  Maybe it’s because my eyes are getting old or maybe it’s because <a href="https://tyler.io/2020/09/surtainly-not/#active-window">the contrast between windows</a> on macOS keeps getting worse. Either way, I built a tiny Mac app last night that draws a border around the active window. I named it “Alan”.
</p></blockquote>
<p>You can <a href="https://github.com/tylerhall/Alan/releases/tag/v1.0">download Alan from the project’s GitHub page</a>.</p>
